{"PROTUBERANCE":[{"def":"That which is protuberant swelled or pushed beyond the surrounding or adjacent surface; a swelling or tumor on the body; a prominence; a bunch or knob; an elevation.","pos":""}],"PROTUBERANCY":[{"def":"The quality or state of being protuberant; protuberance; prominence.","pos":""}],"PROTUBERANT":[{"def":"Prominent, or excessively prominent; bulging beyond the surrounding or adjacent surface; swelling; as, a protuberant joint; a protuberant eye.","pos":""}],"PROTUBERATE":[{"def":"To swell, or be prominent, beyond the adjacent surface; to bulge out.","pos":""}],"PROTUBERATION":[{"def":"The act of swelling beyond the surrounding surface.","pos":""}],"PROTURETER":[{"def":"The duct of a pronephros.","pos":""}]}